posting_body: ['3231 S 204th St, SeaTac, WA 98198', 'Brookstone Apartments are located in the center of SeaTac, Washington, just minutes from the SeaTac International airport, Tukwila Light Rail Station, shopping, restaurants, and schools.', 'The community is located in a peaceful setting surrounded by large evergreen trees.', 'Residents enjoy the fantastic amenities, such as a community swimming pool, hot tub, fitness center, valet trash service, and more.', 'Schedule a tour today and see why residents love calling Brookstone Apartments home!', 'Apartment Features:', 'Ceiling Fan', 'Electric Range', 'Wood Burning Fireplace', 'Private Balcony or Patio', 'Large Closets', 'In Unit Washer & Dryer', 'Community Features:', 'Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent', 'Courtesy Patrol', 'Zero Deposit Community', 'Indoor and Outdoor Pools', 'Covered Parking', 'Pet Friendly', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
